Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.17,0:01:25.08,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}向神问询 是否有误
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.18,0:01:28.20,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}其实不曾孤独过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.37,0:01:30.75,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}其实一直在身旁
