Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.55,0:02:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要很久才开演吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.11,0:02:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要早点去买演唱会的周边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束后再买不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.80,0:02:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人气高的很快就会卖光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.99,0:02:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 其实也挺爱追星的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天见见莎拉不好么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不买T恤 外套之类
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智能机的高性能外壳不能错过！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,0:02:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内含电池 自带高音质线性PCM录音机！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧我知道了 好东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不买吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.16,0:02:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也买的话 不就和你成对了么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.83,0:02:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.41,0:02:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你别买
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得好直白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.15,0:03:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打击人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.77,0:03:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好长的队啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能慢慢排了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.11,0:03:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛傻站着？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 我又不买
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.45,0:03:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不买也是我的伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.47,0:03:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人呆着都没法聊天 不闲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她…应该是讨厌我的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.56,0:03:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招待我看演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起排队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:28.31,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿还没卖完
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.94,0:03:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的关系怎么变好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.62,0:03:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.87,0:03:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 呃…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.64,0:03:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…好长的队啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啦 这可是世界级的当红乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实这点场地根本不够她们开演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.46,0:03:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她…这么厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外壳入手！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看呀看呀看看这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 看这背面印字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.58,0:03:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「ZHIEND」的造型之美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…我也觉得…很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.10,0:04:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是个追星族嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:07.18,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,效果真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:08.77,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帅呆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.96,0:04:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}Lying before me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}Scene painted in green
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}I was never found
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.36,0:04:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}When I played hide & seek
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}A little scar on your face still facing down
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}To the ground you hold yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.42,0:05:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}And crouch like you've been wounded
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}I adored
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}The days when we just fought for things with no means
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}Oh~ I adored
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}When you were always just there for me by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.44,0:05:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种奇妙的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面 我要在这可爱的Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.79,0:05:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解禁这首从未唱过的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Trigger」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}Come now heading to the oblivion
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.65,0:05:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}To the darkness sink me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}Future is lonely as it seems to be
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}And I am reaching from there
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.16,0:06:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得这首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明没有听过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}My mind is clear now
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}I feel like I can do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.21,0:06:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}When I want to do it, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.79,0:06:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}I feel I'm notorious
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.72,0:06:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}Do you know what you can handle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}Do you know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}Spinning round and round
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}Going back and forth
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}Will be here as an angel, that's fallen deep
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}See, there's the dark side waiting for me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}Never end forever
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.14,0:06:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}Out on the rim no need to breathe
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}Even I'm an...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.26,0:06:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}...Think of my sins
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}Forgiveness came to this
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}Fake world where I was dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.25,0:06:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢噢噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.19,0:06:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢噢噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有宇哥哥你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:06:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:06:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZHIEND的新歌太有冲击力了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZHIEND果然厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是首让人永远难忘的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.62,0:07:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管今后发生什么 我都不会忘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.97,0:07:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗哈罗一如既往！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.98,0:07:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D区 晚餐时间到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦！肚子咕咕叫了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:15.25,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.59,0:07:17.72,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D区 晚餐时间到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是这个老爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.18,0:07:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么总是在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古典真好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫不滞涩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.13,0:07:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像算式一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.59,0:07:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你的…妹妹吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.83,0:07:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来还有研究者会怜悯我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.12,0:07:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你总是在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.71,0:07:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突兀的假说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会给研究者造成麻烦的假说 总是被人嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:07:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我沉溺于此处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…呃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道地心说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 知道这词
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.56,0:08:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在看来 这理论如此突兀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在那个年代 却是个很普通的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而事实并非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最先提出异议的人 下场如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被视为异端 被驱逐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.53,0:08:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得不能做任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像现在的我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…呃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！今天吃咖喱的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定又加了激发能力的化学物质
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.69,0:08:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃起来一股药味吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.92,0:08:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我依然觉得咖喱是凝聚了幸福的美味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果隼哥哥也在这里该多好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.30,0:08:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个人一起吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥的能力太过突出了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.74,0:08:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么能力来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:08:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时空移动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:08:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时光回溯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真了不得…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘——！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.79,0:09:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为身怀这了不得的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他才会被关起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼哥哥好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.81,0:09:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.54,0:09:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 不许再谈这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.41,0:09:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开吃喽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依旧是满口药味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.72,0:09:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的能力 能让我入侵对象五秒钟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…他们是这么以为的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.19,0:09:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的能力一旦暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会像哥哥那样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.82,0:09:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被完全剥夺自由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.87,0:09:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 只要我继续接受检查
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们迟早会发现真相
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久违了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.80,0:09:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别回头 安静
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊耳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.55,0:09:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.32,0:09:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到心电感应能力者了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且收发自如
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.96,0:09:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是被关起来了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.17,0:10:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先入侵你右后方的飞机头男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我带来的人 粉碎能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能力不强就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.05,0:10:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜啊 这是咋了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是心电感应能力者的所在地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.46,0:10:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意时机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我们唯一的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦失败 你就会被抹杀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.53,0:10:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也会步上你的后尘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.18,0:10:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊耳那家伙 真的去见那窝囊废了么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.65,0:10:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 七野你嫉妒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.11,0:10:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直在等这一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在这个时刻 弟弟才会动真格
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.18,0:10:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只是个妹控啊 整天都在和妹妹玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才这么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能相信这样的他了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.46,0:11:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这场赌博能有多少胜算呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.71,0:11:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜算得百分百才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许出差错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊 你的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候才能发挥作用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是找出了心电感应能力者哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着瞧 关键时候用给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这可是死亡宣言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.08,0:11:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 少说点话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.81,0:11:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.25,0:11:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的能改变 这个世界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间到 快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放风结束了么 唉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭哭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.66,0:11:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.74,0:11:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你收了什么东西吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.59,0:11:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.34,0:11:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.76,0:11:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的处境为什么和我们如此不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然比不上哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.76,0:11:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的能力也相当厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.38,0:12:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 营救哥哥的行动已准备妥当
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.07,0:12:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就看何时动手了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------TXTB----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的内容已结束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除点名留下的受检者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人请迅速回房
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.57,0:12:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼 我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 这么说来我被点名了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么重要的事 你不早说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.89,0:12:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹没有能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要她留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.72,0:12:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有宇哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步未
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地震了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D区已封锁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请留在原地 等候进一步指示
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.02,0:12:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:55.35,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.51,0:12:57.39,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D区已封锁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:13:00.28,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请留在原地 等候进一步指示
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.37,0:12:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种很不祥的预感…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:12:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快开门
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.33,0:13:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.06,0:13:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.31,0:13:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你…！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.22,0:13:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.54,0:13:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步未怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.50,0:13:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妹妹的能力被强行激发了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能力是「崩毁」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封锁D区
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为那能力毁掉了半个区
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.26,0:13:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步未呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.35,0:13:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 由于能力过于危险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已经被拘束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.83,0:13:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和哥哥一样？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会在解剖之后 抹杀处理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站着不动有什么用？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用你真正的能力 就能救她吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:13:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.28,0:14:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名为「掠夺」的最强能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.20,0:14:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问了 没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 我也要被抹杀了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.93,0:14:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标是心电感应能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.14,0:14:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做到无心 无心 无心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.69,0:14:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有声音传进脑袋…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.30,0:14:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是心电感应吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能看到脸…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.53,0:14:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸…怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 完事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.52,0:14:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.46,0:14:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.85,0:15:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人的记忆 不用抹消吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.86,0:15:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样…最好…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.41,0:15:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.11,0:15:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我出去！放我出去啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.33,0:15:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封锁D区
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回句话！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.67,0:15:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D区出现紧急情况
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全体职员请遵照规定 各就各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.86,0:15:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底出什么事了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都行 快告诉我！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音…连方向都一清二楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.89,0:15:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 能听见我说话吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是有宇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有宇？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吸收了这种能力么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.88,0:15:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果暴露可就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.58,0:15:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事态紧急 迫不得已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.43,0:15:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步未要被解剖了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步未？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.39,0:15:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有了能够毁坏设施的巨大力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.45,0:15:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连步未都…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.11,0:15:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会救出哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.87,0:15:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 快用时光回溯来改变世界吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.14,0:15:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有办法来这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 只要眼睛能捕捉到光…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:15:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七野？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.22,0:16:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死 干嘛要帮你这种妹控…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.75,0:16:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快夺走我的穿透能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.89,0:16:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.86,0:16:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说没时间了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…走！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.85,0:16:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 哥哥一定会改变世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 这个能力…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.28,0:16:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.45,0:16:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接收了七野的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.66,0:16:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就去找你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.54,0:16:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.80,0:17:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见 有宇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.89,0:17:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我必须马上就走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.56,0:17:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.85,0:17:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.41,0:17:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.31,0:17:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了未来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.72,0:17:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.05,0:17:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去改变世界！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抹杀！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.51,0:17:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吓人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.35,0:17:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医院
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在演唱会上昏倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.45,0:17:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步未已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.31,0:17:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做噩梦了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.89,0:17:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.28,0:17:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚我是在做梦吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.79,0:17:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步未不是说过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里好像还有一个成员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好再躺躺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.99,0:18:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能有个哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是真的有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗬 想起来了么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.67,0:18:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「特殊能力搜寻能力者」懂了么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.69,0:18:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 是你啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.67,0:18:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不湿 还挺帅的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.68,0:18:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的梦里 你也出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？我应该是第一次以这种样貌见你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.03,0:18:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊耳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识我哥哥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一到十 全告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别激动 我正是为此而来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.23,0:18:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭上嘴跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.86,0:18:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你心中的疑问全都会消解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.55,0:18:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后你要救一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.21,0:18:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去救你妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.41,0:18:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才 说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.43,0:18:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要由你 去救你妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.15,0:19:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙坂有宇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人都死了 怎么救？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.54,0:19:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该知道你哥哥隼翼有什么能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.55,0:19:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的隼翼先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.53,0:19:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那位隼翼先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.57,0:19:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.48,0:19:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶诶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.04,0:19:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你是他弟弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不像
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.84,0:19:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 能让我也去见见他吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.06,0:19:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们又是什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.45,0:19:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥变成废人后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他给我指明了方向
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.58,0:19:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遇见了唯一可以信赖的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走到了今天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来说的就是我哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.73,0:19:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.37,0:20:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里起 要步行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最不缺的就是钱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.90,0:20:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是个特殊能力者的研究设施
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.54,0:20:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是我们的敌人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.23,0:20:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别废话 跟我走就行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真酷 能录像吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.90,0:20:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.34,0:20:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.23,0:20:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是最后的堡垒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的哥哥 就在里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有宇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久违啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.15,0:21:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人已带到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.02,0:21:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.18,0:21:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是…我哥哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他没想起来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.04,0:21:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前泊消除的那些 似乎都没想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.98,0:21:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.08,0:21:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消除的记忆？那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音 是奈绪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.72,0:21:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是久违了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.37,0:21:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你指明的道路上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.45,0:21:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直走到了今天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.63,0:21:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮了我大忙啊 你做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.86,0:21:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.52,0:21:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.45,0:21:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 有宇呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.12,0:21:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是你大哥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.35,0:22:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感人的重逢 不来个拥抱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.59,0:22:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的脑子…还很乱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.63,0:22:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽是疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.83,0:22:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 这么见外
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.01,0:22:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这也是我自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.47,0:22:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就全说给你听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.30,0:22:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行吗 维尼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.18,0:22:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.57,0:22:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.61,0:22:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就来说说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.70,0:22:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那长而又长的时光回溯历程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.91,0:22:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.23,0:22:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底…要说些什么？
