Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.54,0:23:48.17,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}天空改貌换颜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.23,0:23:51.89,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}群星流转不息
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.95,0:23:55.57,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}待到梦醒之后
